text: Lovey atmosphere and great service. Estella is very professional, very pleasant and gave a great facial. My satisfaction extends beyond my treatment with her. My skin feels sooo amazing and looks younger, brighter after the sessions. To add on, eyelashes were done nicely too! Wendy & Team, keep up the good work! you guys are AMAZING!! ❤️❤️
My facial treatment today was done by Xin Yi. She’s friendly n knowledgeable. Enjoyed throughout the whole process. Feeling relax n refresh now😉

I worked with Elaine from Tampines outlet for a set of misty brows. She was friendly, meticulous and forthcoming when I asked her questions on the products used for the session. I am really pleased with my brows and appreciated how she did not do any promotions during the session, but focused on the brows. I returned to do the classic lashes three times after and also mostly enjoyed my time there. Thank you Elaine and team for the kindness and spectacular service!
I’m pleased with the results. Estella was very gentle and experienced in performing the eye lash extension for me. I highly recommend her to anyone who wants to have this done.

I have had facial treatments at Celmonze@Tampines for more than a decade.

This is my first facial with Agnes, her warm, welcoming service with a smile is contagious. I applaud 👏 her excellent eye, facial massage and meticulous cleansing👍🏻 👍🏻 👍🏻 job Agnes!  👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻 keep up your good works❤️
